      "title": "Parliamentary party leaders will meet again tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs is scheduled to be held tomorrow (15) at 10.00 am at the Parliament complex under the chairmanship of the speaker Mr. Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena to discuss the crisis that has arisen.",
        "It is the third meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs to be held this week.",
        "Chief of Defense Staff General Shavendra Silva, three armed forces commanders and the Inspector General of Police participated in that meeting."
